<br>
When I fought there I completely ignored the casters and just pulled the melee guys, plus the Royal Guardian and the SK Ogre. Using epic, the only guy who can give you problems in the Iksar since he hits pretty hard and fast. Once you kill the melee prisoners, go to the hallway and cast malosi on a guard and run back to the courtyard. Stand there or sit for a few seconds and he'll pop on top of you. <br>
<br>
Rinse, repeat... I made it from 1 yellow into 57 to 59 in 2 days using this method.<br>
<br>
*edit* Epic can handle 1, maybe 2 adds if you have full mana, but the rats hit so hard, it's a struggle. <p>Wentil Stillskin <!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--> Lightbringers<br>
