Casters go more like this.. pull with level 1 burst of flame.<br>
run to pet. back him off a few times.. most of the time the casters are resisted on me. Pet attack when mob is in range.. one BWS(13 second cast time) one Shock of Swords. Dead caster!<br>
same exp for both.. so i tend to choose the casters first. the dorf cleric.. now she will Complete heal from time to time.. but only ever gets a chance to do that once and thats because i picked up a rat or sentry and am avoiding them..<br>
good news about the rats.. at level 57 the rats are LT blue to me.. dubious.<br>
If you leave this area and fight some of the back prisioners.. you do take faction hits.. one of them is it improves faction with the critters of plane of justice.<br>
After playing JP gnolls for a while, the exp in PoJ is about 40% better. <br>
I tend to Duo with a 56 cleric. <br>
I suggest that you do this camp with KEI. and if possible a horse.. although moving away from a rat or sentry can be difficult on horseback. click it off..and run through you pet.. rats tend to pick up on the pet.. if your pet has a DS it will really help to keep the rats attention.<br>
There were a few times, not knowing bout that monk where we had the barb chick and the monk.. <br>
with the cleric partner, doing the monk and the barb chick is easy.. few timely CH's on the pet.. and good to go.. cant stress this enough... DS is a good thing on the earth pet.<br>
At 56 cleric gets about 1 blue for every 8 mobs.. <br>
at 57 i am getting that as well maybe 9 or 10 mobs for the same blue.. but i do have AA on at bout 20% so both bars are moving. <br>
<br>
The basement is doable at 57 but you really need an chanter for slow. Root is nice but they tear up the level 57 earth pet.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wentil>Wentil</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 32<br> <font color=#333333>(1/24/03 1:40:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=334.topic&index=49>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.d.umn.edu/~dander20/untitled.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 1 blue every 20 min in level 57</span><hr size=1> Yes Stren, if you use the method I mentioned above everything will come solo, except when Ssralm Noramir is up, then he will aggro also because he has a wide aggro range and all the mobs run past him up the stairs.<br>
