<br>
Never got a single add unless Sralm was up.<br>
<br>
If Sralm's up, kill him first, and then you won't get adds.<br>
<br>
Chaincasting is unnecessary. Take your 57 earth and cycle transon's on your pet, and nukes on Sralm. Get KEI.<br>
<br>
Also, kill the warrior ones first, easiest ones to take out because they don't nuke you all the way back to the courtyard.<br>
<br>
I also suggest, if you're taking out the female gnome mage, or Zenoux the drake wizard...Get your MR/FR/CR up. Elemental blanket, elemental cloak work perfectly for this.<br>
<br>
The gnome cleric female resists often, even without self buffing.<br>
<br>
There's no real risk involved if you plan accordingly. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=qaedainmagikot@themagicianstower>Qaedain Magikot</A> at: 2/13/03 2:50:43 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rishid>rishid</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#333333>(2/18/03 9:46:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=334.topic&index=58>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 1 blue every 20 min in level 57</span><hr size=1> But is the experience better then Katta Guards? <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm24.showMessageRange?topicID=334.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm24.showMessageRange?topicID=334.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm24.showPrevMessage?topicID=334.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm24.showNextMessage?topicID=334.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=334.topic&index=58><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm24.threadControl?topicID=334.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a>